  <body region="amara-subtitle-area">
    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:30.597" end="00:00:34.582">&#65279;&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:47.142" end="00:00:50.384">$$ Year 6 of the AIDS epidemic. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.784" end="00:00:59.556">$$ Greenwich Village, New York City.<br/>The epicenter. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:07.092" end="00:01:12.569">$$ With no drugs to treat the disease,<br/>AIDS is nearly 100% fatal. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:12.569" end="00:01:16.446">$$ Panic drives a backlash<br/>of blame and anti-gay violence. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:16.446" end="00:01:19.323">$$ Even hospitals<br/>routinely turn away the dying. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:26.127" end="00:01:28.791">$$ Fighting for their lives,<br/>patients and their advocates $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:28.791" end="00:01:30.993">$$ take matters into their own hands. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:31.627" end="00:01:34.407">- Welcome to ACT UP. We are <br/>the AIDS Coalition</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34.407" end="00:01:36.638">- [together] to unleash power.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:36.638" end="00:01:40.052">A diverse, non-partisan group<br/>and individuals united in anger</p>
      <p begin="00:01:40.052" end="00:01:42.105">and committed to direct action</p>
      <p begin="00:01:42.105" end="00:01:44.130">-[together] to end the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44.130" end="00:01:51.674">- In less than 12 hours from now,<br/>we are gonna be taking over City Hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:51.966" end="00:01:54.123">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.123" end="00:01:55.843">[Crowd chanting]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:55.843" end="00:01:58.111">- [Ed Koch] Yes.<br/>- *[male reporter] Mr. Mayor,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:58.111" end="00:01:59.280">in campaigning <br/>for the lesbian and gay vote,*</p>
      <p begin="00:01:59.280" end="00:02:02.084">in an election year, a bit of<br/>historical context is necessary</p>
      <p begin="00:02:02.084" end="00:02:04.184">in dealing with the AIDS crisis<br/>in New York City.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.184" end="00:02:06.238">It wasn't until 1983 that you met</p>
      <p begin="00:02:06.238" end="00:02:08.306">with people to deal with<br/>the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.306" end="00:02:09.513">How do you respond to these questions?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09.513" end="00:02:10.690">- [Ed] That it's a falsehood.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.690" end="00:02:13.446">- Please, anybody who's<br/>thinking about being arrested,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.446" end="00:02:17.982">*fill out a support sheet, make sure<br/>your support person knows who you are*</p>
      <p begin="00:02:18.028" end="00:02:20.235">and what group you're in.<br/>Yeah?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:20.404" end="00:02:25.894">- Um, if we end up in The Tombs,<br/>is there like a queer tank there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.894" end="00:02:28.897">and would you recommend that we<br/>ask to be there?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.897" end="00:02:31.484">- There is a homo tank<br/>and I've been there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:31.484" end="00:02:33.834">and it's better than the straight tank,<br/>let me tell you.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.834" end="00:02:35.000">- [Ed] Who else? Yes?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:35.000" end="00:02:38.663">- [reporter] In the past,<br/>you've described ACT UP as fascist</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.663" end="00:02:40.736">yet in the press release, <br/>you called them concerned citizen.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.736" end="00:02:43.215">*I was wondering <br/>what changed your mind?*</p>
      <p begin="00:02:43.215" end="00:02:45.815">- [Ed] I don't think <br/>that you can't use both.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.815" end="00:02:48.571">Fascist can be concerned citizens.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:49.709" end="00:02:55.882">And I don't believe they are fascist.<br/>I think they have used the fascist tactic.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.882" end="00:03:00.336">- Let us celebrate together<br/>tonight, the end of the last day</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.336" end="00:03:02.646">on which Ed Koch can tell himself</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.646" end="00:03:06.284">that the communities which are <br/>being decimated by this epidemic</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.284" end="00:03:09.521">are so weak and so divided <br/>among themselves</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.521" end="00:03:12.205">that he can keep serving us<br/>this kind of bullshit.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.205" end="00:03:12.979">[laughter]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:13.042" end="00:03:15.723">Tomorrow morning, he will begin<br/>to learn the truth.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:15.723" end="00:03:17.415">[applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.330" end="00:03:21.889">- [Female voice] ACT UP, stand tall<br/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:21.889" end="00:03:25.846">- [Crowd] ACT UP, stand tall<br/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:25.846" end="00:03:29.692">ACT UP, stand tall,<br/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:29.692" end="00:03:31.515">ACT UP, stand tall...</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.515" end="00:03:35.133">&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.728" end="00:03:41.784">$$ City Hall $$</p>
      <p begin="00:04:03.176" end="00:04:06.061">*- [male reporter] We're talking <br/>to Jim Eigo*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:06.061" end="00:04:09.161">*for the Treatment Issues Committee<br/>of ACT UP.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:09.161" end="00:04:10.520">Jim, what specific treatment issues</p>
      <p begin="00:04:10.520" end="00:04:13.020">are pretty important <br/>in this demonstration this week?</p>
      <p begin="00:04:13.020" end="00:04:16.390">*- [Jim Eigo] The municipal hospitals<br/>are totally falling apart.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.390" end="00:04:19.309">*More than half the people<br/>who get diagnosed with AIDS today*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.309" end="00:04:22.691">*get diagnosed in the emergency rooms<br/>of our city.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:22.691" end="00:04:24.826">You're going to find yourself <br/>waiting four days</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.826" end="00:04:27.676">in an emergency room before<br/>you get a bed.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.946" end="00:04:31.936">- I'm pretty scared about being <br/>HIV positive.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.990" end="00:04:33.578">I don't have much choice in the matter.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.578" end="00:04:34.801">- I just love all these people</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.801" end="00:04:37.528">and I think that what we're <br/>doing is really right.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.528" end="00:04:40.835">And -- I mean, listen to this <br/>and look at our people,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.835" end="00:04:42.487">it's just really wonderful</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.487" end="00:04:44.363">and it's worth putting<br/>*ourselves on the line. *</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.363" end="00:04:46.576">- *[Ann Northrop] There is<br/>no accurate diagnosis.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.576" end="00:04:48.537">*There are incentives<br/>in the city hospitals*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:48.537" end="00:04:50.560">*not to diagnose people with AIDS,*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:50.560" end="00:04:53.146">and therefore people don't get treated.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:53.146" end="00:04:56.556">We are angry at the way this city<br/>has handled this crisis</p>
      <p begin="00:04:56.556" end="00:05:00.138">and we demand that Ed Koch<br/>exert leadership</p>
      <p begin="00:05:00.138" end="00:05:02.720">and declare a state of emergency.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:02.743" end="00:05:04.128">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:04.128" end="00:05:07.360">*- [Peter] Go on the street now or wait,<br/>those are the options.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:07.360" end="00:05:08.987">One. He says go.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.987" end="00:05:09.997">*-Two, now.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:09.997" end="00:05:11.157">-He says now, three.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:11.434" end="00:05:12.233">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Don?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:12.449" end="00:05:13.478">*Go now--*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.478" end="00:05:15.239">*-[Reporter] I'm standing here<br/>with Larry Kramer*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:15.293" end="00:05:17.672">*What is ACT UP trying to say today<br/>to Ed Koch?*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:17.672" end="00:05:19.890">-We're sending a message<br/>to public officials,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:19.890" end="00:05:23.638">to closeted public officials<br/>that we won't be shot down anymore</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23.638" end="00:05:25.538">and obviously all the AIDS issues.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:25.538" end="00:05:27.761">*-I would love to see, like,<br/>more cameras or something *</p>
      <p begin="00:05:27.761" end="00:05:29.522">you know, for our own protection.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:29.522" end="00:05:30.867">*-[male voice] and everyone here <br/>has concerns--*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.867" end="00:05:33.331">*-[Larry] People die everyday.<br/>Friends get sick everyday.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:33.331" end="00:05:35.701">*I don't--it's like being in the trenches.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:35.701" end="00:05:39.273">*There's such anger in the community<br/>and that it's coalescing in a way *</p>
      <p begin="00:05:39.273" end="00:05:41.757">that has never been done before.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.757" end="00:05:43.564">- Okay, which way do we face girlfriends?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.564" end="00:05:45.448">This way or that way?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:45.448" end="00:05:47.494">[crowd talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.517" end="00:05:51.480">[cars honking]<br/>[crowd cheering and rallying]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:51.480" end="00:05:54.344">[together] HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54.436" end="00:05:58.052">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:58.052" end="00:06:01.543">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01.543" end="00:06:05.261">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:05.304" end="00:06:07.280">- [police officer talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:07.295" end="00:06:11.724">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:14.549" end="00:06:16.789">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.585" end="00:06:49.724">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49.823" end="00:06:52.849">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15.513" end="00:07:18.500">$ How To Survive A Plague. $</p>
      <p begin="00:07:27.693" end="00:07:30.238">- I guess, I'm feeling pretty hopeless<br/>at the moment.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:30.238" end="00:07:37.303">I think that the biggest question that<br/>I'm facing now is how to remain hopeful</p>
      <p begin="00:07:37.303" end="00:07:40.229">in the face of increasing loss.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:40.659" end="00:07:43.456">- *[David Barr] I don't know,<br/>maybe it sounds really corny *</p>
      <p begin="00:07:43.456" end="00:07:44.302">but I--</p>
      <p begin="00:07:47.101" end="00:07:50.876">as difficult as the time is for us,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:52.594" end="00:07:59.950">I like being alive. And I love my friends <br/>and I love my family.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:00.011" end="00:08:04.555">*I love people around me.*<br/>- This, I'm gonna die from this.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:04.593" end="00:08:09.174">This isn't gonna be cured for<br/>years and years and years and years.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:09.174" end="00:08:10.811">*- Doctor's office?*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.811" end="00:08:12.371">- [speaking in the phone] <br/>Hi, it's Peter Staley.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:12.371" end="00:08:14.315">It's like living in a war.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:14.315" end="00:08:17.891">All around me,<br/>friends are dropping dead.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:18.016" end="00:08:21.668">And you're scared for your own life<br/>all at the same time.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:24.044" end="00:08:27.753">*I was diagnosed with AIDS-related complex*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:27.753" end="00:08:31.051">*while I was working as a bond trader<br/>on Wall Street.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:31.359" end="00:08:33.190">*I had night sweats.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:33.190" end="00:08:38.163">*I began to get dry, patchy, scaly,<br/>itchy skin on my face. *</p>
      <p begin="00:08:38.246" end="00:08:40.729">*And I would get sick constantly.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:40.729" end="00:08:43.745">*Colds would lay me up for weeks.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:44.323" end="00:08:48.053">I started to look around in desperation</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48.707" end="00:08:56.623">for ways that I could find treatments<br/>to help save my life.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:59.392" end="00:09:04.375">And there was nothing coming out of our<br/>government's efforts, I quickly realized.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:09.255" end="00:09:14.485">*Everything I read said I had about<br/>two years to live, at most. *</p>
      <p begin="00:09:16.639" end="00:09:19.951">[Crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:20.690" end="00:09:22.878">$ ACT UPS first protest<br/>March 24, 1987 $</p>
      <p begin="00:09:22.878" end="00:09:24.734">*-[male voice] WHAT DO WE WANT?*<br/>*-[crowd answering] A CURE!*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:24.734" end="00:09:26.791">*-[male voice] WHEN DO WE WANT IT?*<br/>*-[crowd answering] NOW!*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:26.791" end="00:09:29.223">*-[Peter] I was on my way to work*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:29.233" end="00:09:32.274">*and I got handed <br/>a flier about ACT UP and AIDS.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:32.284" end="00:09:36.490">*My mentor says, "If you ask me,<br/>I think they all deserve to die" *</p>
      <p begin="00:09:36.490" end="00:09:38.511">*"because they took it up their butt."*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:38.770" end="00:09:43.850">*I was deeply closeted and I had to just <br/>stew about it for the rest of the day.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:46.726" end="00:09:49.562">*I got myself to the very next <br/>ACT UP meeting.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:49.675" end="00:09:53.132">*They could just tap into that<br/>immediate anger and get stuff done.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:53.132" end="00:09:55.702">*-[female voice] We need to get approval <br/>on this...*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:55.702" end="00:09:59.208">*This is a non-violent <br/>and quiet kiss-in.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:59.208" end="00:10:02.117">We will not leave until<br/>the administrator meets with us</p>
      <p begin="00:10:02.117" end="00:10:07.024">and tells us that Saint Vincent's<br/>is willing to make a public statement</p>
      <p begin="00:10:07.024" end="00:10:09.274">condemning gay and lesbian violence.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:09.274" end="00:10:12.243">[crowd cheering and applauding]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:15.282" end="00:10:17.289">- All those in favor?</p>
      <p begin="00:10:19.023" end="00:10:21.137">*-All those oppose?*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:21.384" end="00:10:23.078">[car passing]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:24.366" end="00:10:27.003">*-[male voice] They're coming.*<br/>*You see that right there.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:27.225" end="00:10:29.939">*You've heard of ACT UP,<br/>you've seen our flyers.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:29.939" end="00:10:32.388">*The kiss-in happens tonight.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:32.396" end="00:10:34.249">*-[male voice] ACT UP, FIGHT BACK.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:34.249" end="00:10:37.491">*Take gloves, ACT UP. Woo, woo.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:39.258" end="00:10:41.158">*-[male voice] I'll deal with the camera.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:41.158" end="00:10:43.592">*-[female voice] Are your own<br/>security guards ever beat people up here?*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:43.592" end="00:10:45.960">[people chattering]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:52.656" end="00:10:55.662">- Members of the mainstream media<br/>were thrown out as we were</p>
      <p begin="00:10:55.662" end="00:10:59.407">earlier on but Steve and I<br/>came back in and we'll bring you</p>
      <p begin="00:10:59.407" end="00:11:00.982">this exclusive footage inside...</p>
      <p begin="00:11:00.982" end="00:11:03.051">- Don't destroy property, <br/>you're destroying property, okay?</p>
      <p begin="00:11:03.051" end="00:11:05.652">- Actually, you've damaged<br/>some human property last week.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:05.705" end="00:11:09.084">- You will not beat up on faggots<br/>and you will not beat up on lesbians</p>
      <p begin="00:11:09.084" end="00:11:12.472">in hospitals in our own community.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:12.472" end="00:11:15.237">- Two gay women were beaten up,<br/>and when her lover came to respond,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:15.237" end="00:11:16.660">*you know the story. *</p>
      <p begin="00:11:16.660" end="00:11:19.970">*And another story was, two gay guys came,<br/>and one was sick with AIDS. *</p>
      <p begin="00:11:19.970" end="00:11:22.156">*The security guard told him <br/>to get the fuck out of here*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:22.156" end="00:11:23.763">*and called him, "Faggot."*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:23.763" end="00:11:26.021">I think if you're gonna work,<br/>especially in Greenwich Village,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:26.021" end="00:11:29.421">you should have some sensitivity training<br/>because we're not gonna have it.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:29.421" end="00:11:31.891">- I'm willing to meet with three people,<br/>the rest of you leave.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:31.967" end="00:11:34.129">[crowd chattering]</p>
      <p begin="00:11:34.874" end="00:11:37.051">- It's unclear how to play it.<br/>My own instinct would be to say,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:37.459" end="00:11:40.968">"We'd be glad to meet with you<br/>when the meeting is over, we'll leave".</p>
      <p begin="00:11:41.283" end="00:11:43.832">Not to leave before the meeting<br/>takes place.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:43.832" end="00:11:44.950">- Gregg?</p>
      <p begin="00:11:44.950" end="00:11:47.675">- We show the kind of power we can have<br/>by immediate action, by sticking together,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:47.675" end="00:11:49.636">by reaching a consensus together.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:49.636" end="00:11:51.611">We should take the same steps,<br/>we should be cool headed.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:51.611" end="00:11:53.212">- I'm gonna take a straw poll, okay?</p>
      <p begin="00:11:53.212" end="00:11:55.727">*And we agreed to leave the waiting room*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:55.727" end="00:11:58.662">*while he met with <br/>three of our representatives,*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:58.662" end="00:12:02.135">*Gregg, Jerry and Neil<br/>in that public space right there.*</p>
      <p begin="00:12:02.196" end="00:12:06.388">And then we would sit around out here<br/>and wait for the outcome.</p>
